column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.pmRa, p.pmDec, p.pmraerr, p.pmdecerr, p.nfit FROM #x x, #upload u, ProperMotions p WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID=p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
